title: 1949–50 Cardiff City F.C. season
text:
The 1949–50 season was <a href="Cardiff%20City%20F.C.">Cardiff City F.C.</a>'s 23rd season in the <a href="The%20Football%20League">Football League</a>. They competed in the 22-team <a href="Football%20League%20Second%20Division">Division Two</a>, then the second tier of <a href="Football%20in%20England">English football</a>, finishing tenth.
